In this project, different AI-powered tools were used at specific stages of the software development lifecycle. Each tool was selected based on its strengths and used as a support mechanism, while the core design decisions and implementations were carried out by the developer.

- DeepSeek

Used mainly during the implementation phase

Assisted in understanding complex logic and refining task workflows

Helped with algorithmic thinking and feature implementation strategies

- Cursor AI

Used during the coding phase

