Helped visualize role-based dashboards before Swing implementation

- Slidesgo

Used for preparing the final presentation slides

Provided structured and professional slide templates

Improved the visual quality and organization of the project presentation

- Google Gemini

Used during the report writing and presentation preparation

Assisted in improving explanations, wording, and structure

